    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"feline-legacy\">Feline Legacy</h3><p>Ninja cats are rarely seen outside their homeland. The reason for this rarity is uncertain, but a unique genetic mutation found in seemingly random domestic cat breeds awakens an intellect far surpassing that of a normal feline. Over the years, as more of these extraordinary cats emerged, they united to form what would become the Ninneko Clan, leaving their distinctive paw print on the shinobi world!</p><h4 id=\"ninneko-traits\">Ninneko Traits</h4><hr /><ul><li><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Dex, +1 Cha</li><li><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 35 feet, and you have a climbing speed equal to your walking speed.</li><li><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Acrobatics, Perception</li><li><strong>Darkvision:</strong> You have darkvision to a range of 60 feet.</li><li><strong>Extra Language:</strong> Cat-Speak, you can speak to and understand feline creatures.</li></ul>",
